OL,5, Post Office campaigner Alan Bates has  
OL,6, slammed the firm as a "toxic           
OL,7, organisation" that "cannot get its act 
OL,8, together".                             
OL,10,FMr Bates said financial redress for    
OL,11,Fsub-postmasters is "the real priority" 
OL,12,Fas the firm's bosses are engulfed in a 
OL,13,Frow with the former chairman.          
OL,15,FThe former sub-postmaster Alan Bates   
OL,16,Fled the campaign to expose the Post    
OL,17,FOffice Horizon IT scandal.             
OL,19,FHis work partly inspired the recent ITV
OL,20,Fdrama which reignited public interest. 
